&lt;h3&gt;WHAT YOU WILL NEED TO SUCCEED&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You must have profound knowledge and experience in blockchain technology, software engineering, and decentralized software architecture and a passion for building and continuously improving what seeks to be the best crypto custody solution in the market. You have experience working with digital-currency custody, blockchain, or cryptography. You can work with numerous cross-functional teams in a fast-paced, growing company. You have a working knowledge of Docker, multi-sig wallets, NFTs, and other standard digital wallets and security paradigms. You have a proven track record of delivering and owning web-scale pipelines systems in production. You love the blockchain technology, want to bring it to the masses, and enjoy delving into novel emerging technologies like MPC (Multi-party Computation).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A plus is technical knowledge of elliptic-curve cryptography, multiparty party computation and privacy-enhancing technologies, layer2-technologies, compilers, and virtual machines.&amp;nbsp; Another advantage is experience with financial institutes in a regulated environment.&lt;/p&gt;
