&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;In this role, you will be executing on a strategy for delivering permissioned blockchains at scale. You will be working with ConsenSys Quorum and Azure technologies to deliver Quorum Blockchain Service and related capabilities. You will be working on projects and cross team initiatives for which you will have to be proficient at creating and maintaining warm and productive working relationships with other teams. Additionally, you will mentor other team members to design and deliver world class solutions that our customers will love.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
